item.title: CVE-2019-5281|2024-08-04T19:54:51.806Z -- huawei -- huawei%20y9%202019
item.description: There is an information leak vulnerability in some Huawei phones, versions earlier than Jackman-L21 8.2.0.155(C185R1P2). When a local attacker uses the camera of a smartphone, the attacker can exploit this vulnerability to obtain sensitive information by performing a series of operations.
